Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:05.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s been dead less than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:09.50,Signs,,0,0,0,,Naoko Kuroe (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was probably strangled then put in this net....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:14.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The footprints on the sand are from sandals and boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoko-{\i1}san{\i0} was probably wearin’ guest sandals from the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so the boots must belong to the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:20.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would anyone do this to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:21.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here’s your answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:26.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Somebody stepped on an Arrow of Dugong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:28.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the sandal prints,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:30.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoko-{\i1}san{\i0} must’ve dropped it and stepped on it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while she was struggling with the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the killer was after the arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:41.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we follow the boot prints, we’ll find the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:45.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... The prints...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...go straight into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:50.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something shiny around the prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:04.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Scales...from a fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:09.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a couple scales on Naoko-{\i1}san{\i0}’s clothes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:17.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigating the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:20.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the job of the Fukui Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:23.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you’ve finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer's footprints disappeared into the sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... and left some fish scales behind too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you say fish scales...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not saying the killer's a mermaid...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mermaids don't wear rubber boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer probably approached from the shoreline and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then went up to the nets where Naoko was told to wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After murdering Naoko, the killer walked back to the shoreline
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And left the scene walking through the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, did anyone see Naoko leave the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:02.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,Not me ... she wasn't there when I got there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:02.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kimie Shimabukuro (27)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:07.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,Benzo Kadowaki (52)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:07.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,Rokuro Fukuyama (27)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,Benzo, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.31,Signs,,0,0,0,,You signed in right after Naoko, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,I didn't see her and nobody was in the room when I got there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means Naoko was the first one to get here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then she left to go where the nets were hung...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you think the same person who killed Toshimi Killed Naoko too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know that for sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we do know the killer took Naoko's arrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dugong's arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before she disappeared, Saori also said that she'd lost her arrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah ... she might already be dead too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw Saori near the Mermaid's waterfall on the morning of yesterday's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was far away and I only cought a glance, she was in the forest by the waterfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are absolutely sure it was Saori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No mistake, She was the only girl with brown hair and glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she always wears blue clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:04.50,Signs,,0,0,0,,Then she must be running away from something,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:07.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,Saori Kadowaki (27)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:07.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,That's why she's hiding from everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr.Kadowaki, don't you have any idea what's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me... she never told me anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just hope she hasn't turned into a mermaid like this dead girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mermaid? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The legendary nun ate the meat of the mermaid that was cought in the net...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}M-Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the arrow leaves your body, evil will overtake you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,women will return to the water and become silent mermaids...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ka-Kazuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind that, let's all go look for Saori in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay close to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.95,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}After that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:06.24,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}the police searched everybody at the funeral,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.44,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}to see if the killer who stole Naoko-{\i1}san{\i0}’s arrow was still among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.78,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But the only people with arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.25,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}were Benzo-{\i1}san{\i0} and Kazuha, who’d won them at the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:19.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kudo. Got any leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:24.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All I’ve noticed is that Toshimi-{\i1}san{\i0} and Naoko-{\i1}san{\i0}, the two confirmed victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and Saori-{\i1}san{\i0}, who’s missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:30.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,all believed in Lady Mikoto’s powers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:33.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and were obsessed with the Arrow of Dugong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. {\i1}Too{\i0} obsessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:41.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we only knew who had which ticket at last night’s festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have everyone sign a list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come with me now and have a look at the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Pull yourself together, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this isn’t the best time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but have you thought about what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m serious, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:10.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not after Toshimi’s death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:18.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can’t leave this island and abandon Great-Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:27.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So all five of you went to school together, even college?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all big movie fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:33.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so in college we joined the film club,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and made our own film, “The Legend of Bikuni”!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:41.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When it won the gold medal at a film festival, we were so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were ready to go to Hollywood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:50.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, none of us could forget the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:54.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought Toshimi and Naoko would end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:57.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, that’s strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:01.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure I kept it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s gone... Just this year’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:08.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the old lady took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else knew the entry books were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the locals, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:19.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll look through the other rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:22.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The old foreign minister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the director of the Secretariat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the president of the Bank of Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they all wanted to live forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Shiho Miyano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:47.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Isn’t that... {\i1}her{\i0} real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.55,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Nah, it can’t be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:52.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She’s not the type who’d care about eternal youth and beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:57.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just saw her! A woman with light hair and glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was starin’ at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:07.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saori-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is this glass cracked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s Kimie-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:16.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to look through the new warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s the warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it was behind the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:23.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, check out that glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It couldn’t be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.12,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The warehouse kept burning through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:31.51,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It burned to the ground, just like it did three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:37.35,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes, just like three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.35,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}there was a body inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A burned body!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right... it was burned beyond recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it had glasses on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could just barely make out that it was wearing blue clothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably... Saori... who was missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-Then the girl we saw last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was a gh-ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kimie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:01.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kimie... where are you, Kimie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:02.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mikoto Shimabukuro (130)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:04.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kimie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't Kimie back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, she's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go stay with the great grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,didn't Kimie say she went to the dentist recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you know what are you implying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't fool me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same thought passed through your mind too, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We both have the same bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:35.43,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Half a Day Later
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:34.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see... Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:39.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How’d it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:44.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They compared the teeth of the burnt body with Kimie-{\i1}san{\i0}’s dental records.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were a perfect match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That cannot be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimie-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kimie has died...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:11.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, old  lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer swooped in the minute we took our eyes off her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:16.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another innocent young life snuffed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:20.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while an old fool like me lives on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:24.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, remember when you moved the mermaid’s grave into the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:27.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:32.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person has left this world as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:37.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:44.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of case is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t have a suspect or a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, we don't even know why Kimie was dressed like Saori...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that was probably to make us think it was Saori who died...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the killer must be Saori...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:04.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or it could be someone who wants us to think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the ocean's right behind us last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kimie told us that... last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, no matter who the killer is, one thing is for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to find the killer as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't let such a heartless killer run free!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:38.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:40.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone just called Kimie-{\i1}san{\i0}’s place,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the person on the other end said something weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:45.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,“Thank you very much for selling us the arrow.”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:49.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,“It was well worth the million yen. Our son’s operation was a success!”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They bought an arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For a million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:59.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They said a man who worked at the shrine sold it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:05.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it was that old couple who cancelled their tickets on the morning of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:06.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But who was the guy who sold them the arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn’t know his name,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:13.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but they said he was a big guy, about 50 years old, with a stubby beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:13.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Benzo-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! If it was before the festival, then that arrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More than likely it was the arrow Saori said she lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And lucky for Benzo, he won an arrow at the festival and on top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the register with all the names got lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoko, who was killed on the day of Toshimi's wake, also
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,had her arrow stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the Ebihara's home where the wake was held.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo, I mean... Mr.Mouri, please go and check Benzo's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:56.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Benzo-{\i1}san{\i0} left last night right after we did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:59.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He went running out, looking pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:02.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just like I thought. Benzo-{\i1}san{\i0} overheard us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:06.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He heard us talkin’ about goin’ down to Kimie-{\i1}san{\i0}’s house to look at that notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so he beat us there and stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it was probably Benzo who set fire to the warehouse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're probably right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Kimie found him hanging around holding the registry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you forgot !
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are the one who told me to stay close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, since I have an arrow that's been blessed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm your good luck charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about, if you're in danger, I'll protect you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm so lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm serious... Heiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:46.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Kimie-{\i1}chan{\i0} has died, I guess this year’s Dugong Festival will be the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:56.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you show us again which footprints are yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:58.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:05.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:10.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A dent on the bottom of the sandal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:11.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It’s still fresh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are the sandals Naoko was wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were taken to the Fukui Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:21.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuha, lend me that arrow of yours, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A perfect match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:32.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is the sandal that stepped on the Arrow of Dugong on the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:35.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It’s just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw rats! I knew it, no one's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you people doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, we wanted to talk to Benzo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him since the wake last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What bad timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we thought at least we could take a look at the missing Saori's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to get inside, take a look under the potted plant
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where the key is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha, I found it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's alright to go in without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't mind, we'll just have a fast look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how did Saori act just before she disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... well,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was scared, even when the ocean got rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she said mermaid was going to punish her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Punish her...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here’s Saori’s room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aspirin, toothbrush...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saori’s run-away kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:49.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She usually just stayed over at Kimie’s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:52.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She left clothes and an extra pair of glasses there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you mean... the clothes Kimie was wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when she was found in the warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she could have put them on herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How stupid, why'd she have to go and do that for...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe to lure the killer out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha... that's ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if Kimie thought the killer was after Saori too
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and if she saw someone suspicious hanging around the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she might have done what Conan said so that she could catch the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,last night during the fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,didn't you say you saw someone who looked like Saori in the yard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:31.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is there a photo of Saori-{\i1}san{\i0} around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a photo album somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran, was this the person you saw in the garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:41.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know. It was dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:46.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these photos from the time you guys made your own movie about the legendary nun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:47.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:49.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:52.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:56.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really looks like a mermaid’s swimming in the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:19:00.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... And this storm scene looks so real...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:03.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The movie won at the film festival
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:06.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,mostly because of Saori’s visual effects and Kimie’s special-effects make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but 1 year after that, there really was a storm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and both of Kimie's parents, as well as mine and Saori's mother were lost at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not one of us dreamed anything like that would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:28.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Her account book, bank card, name seal, driver’s license and passport are all here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but I can’t find one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:31.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It couldn’t be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:47.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kudo—I mean, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:50.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing. I was just about to phone ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.20,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Remember the sandal prints on the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.30,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I found a sandal with a dent mark\Nfrom stepping on an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.75,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It proves the killer left the funeral room,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:01.89,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}walked out to the fishing net where Naoko-{\i1}san{\i0} was waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:04.84,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}killed her, then went back to the room again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:10.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only two people who could’ve done that were Benzo-{\i1}san{\i0}, and Rokuro-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:14.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But seeing how upset Rokuro-{\i1}san{\i0} was that afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I find it hard to believe he’d hurt Kimie-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.27,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means the killer’s gotta be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:24.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori, here’s my deduction. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:26.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:45.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! That’s crazy talk!\NI ain’t gonna swallow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:50.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have eliminated the impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:53.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever remains, however improbable,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:56.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,must be the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:57.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:02.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve located Benzo Kadowaki on the mountain! We’re in pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Let’s go, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:07.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I’ll hook up with ya after we arrest Benzo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:08.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:09.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to believe it either, Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It’s not true! It can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:23.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I’m not buyin’ it, Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:25.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell incense?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:29.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya kiddin’ me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:31.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’d burn incense up here on the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}“Danger - Cliff Ahead”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The grave of that so-called mermaid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:49.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If that’s the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:53.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The person Kudo fingered...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:56.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}really is the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:01.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:16.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuha!
